Package: linaldb
Type: Package
Title: R Client for LINALDB
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("gorigami", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R client for LINALDB, a SQL-inspired analytical engine
    treating vectors, matrices, and tensors as first-class citizens.
    Talks to a running 'linal serve' instance over its HTTP API
    (POST /execute for ad-hoc DSL, /delivery/* for real Parquet dataset
    export). Scaffolding only as of this version -- see
    PYTHON_R_INTEROP_PLAN.md (checkpoints 3-4) in the parent repository
    for the real client implementation and clients/CONTRACT.md for the
    wire contract this package implements against.
License: LinalDB Community License v1.0 (see ../../LICENSE; not a
    standard SPDX/CRAN-recognized license string yet -- fine for
    scaffolding, revisit before any real CRAN submission)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    arrow
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
